gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 137, Wizards 114
gameRecap.excerpt: Jalen Green ties his career high with 42 points, along with 10 rebounds and seven 3PT FG to lead the Rockets over the Wizards, 137-114. Amen Thompson added 25 points and 10 rebounds in the victory, while Corey Kispert tallied 16 points for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Rockets win their sixth consecutive game and improve to 33-35 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 11-58.
